  <entry>
    <title>上机实践 一</title>
    <url>/2023/11/21/%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%BA%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5-%E4%B8%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Java入门"><a href="#Java入门" class="headerlink" title="Java入门"></a>Java入门</h1><h2 id="实验一-一个简单的应用程序"><a href="#实验一-一个简单的应用程序" class="headerlink" title="实验一 一个简单的应用程序"></a>实验一 一个简单的应用程序</h2><h3 id="目的"><a href="#目的" class="headerlink" title="目的"></a>目的</h3><p>掌握开发 Java 应用程序的 3 个步骤，即编写源文件、编译源文件和运行应用程序。</p>
<h3 id="要求"><a href="#要求" class="headerlink" title="要求"></a>要求</h3><p>编写一个简单的 Java 应用程序，该程序在命令行窗口输出两行文字，即”你好，欢迎学习Java“和”We are students“。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="源码"><a href="#源码" class="headerlink" title="源码"></a>源码</h3><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Hello</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;   <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span> <span class="params">(String args[ ])</span></span><br><span class="line">     &#123;  <span class="comment">//【代码1】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;你好，很高兴学习Java</span></span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;你好，欢迎学习Java&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">         A a=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">A</span>();<span class="comment">//为对象a分配变量</span></span><br><span class="line">         a.fA();</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;    <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">fA</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">      &#123;  <span class="comment">//【代码2】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;We are students&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;We are students&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="程序运行效果"><a href="#程序运行效果" class="headerlink" title="程序运行效果"></a>程序运行效果</h3><p><img src="data:image;base64,"></p>
<h3 id="记"><a href="#记" class="headerlink" title="记"></a>记</h3><p>打开命令行窗口：徽标键+R，输入cmd进入</p>
<p>命令行窗口进入文件夹目录：cd 路径</p>
<p>编译命令：javac Hello.java</p>
<p>运行命令：java Hello</p>
<h2 id="实验二-联合编译"><a href="#实验二-联合编译" class="headerlink" title="实验二 联合编译"></a>实验二 联合编译</h2><h3 id="目的-1"><a href="#目的-1" class="headerlink" title="目的"></a>目的</h3><p>学习同时编译多个 Java 源文件</p>
<h3 id="要求-1"><a href="#要求-1" class="headerlink" title="要求"></a>要求</h3><p>编写 4 个源文件，即 MainClass.java、A.java、B.java 和 C.java，每个源文件只有一个类。MainClass.java 含有应用程序的主类（含由 main() 方法），并使用了 A、B 和 C 类。将 4 个源文件保存到同一目录中，例如”C:\1000“,然后编译 MainClass.java。</p>
<h3 id="源码-1"><a href="#源码-1" class="headerlink" title="源码"></a>源码</h3><h4 id="MainClass"><a href="#MainClass" class="headerlink" title="MainClass"></a>MainClass</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">MainClass</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span> <span class="params">(String args[ ])</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">       <span class="comment">//【代码1】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;你好，只需编译我&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">         System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;你好，欢迎学习 Java&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">A</span> <span class="variable">a</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">A</span>();<span class="comment">//为对象a分配变量</span></span><br><span class="line">        a.fA();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">B</span> <span class="variable">b</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">B</span>();<span class="comment">//为对象b分配变量</span></span><br><span class="line">        b.fB();</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="A"><a href="#A" class="headerlink" title="A"></a>A</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">A</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">fA</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 【代码2】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;I am A&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;I am A&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="B"><a href="#B" class="headerlink" title="B"></a>B</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">B</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">fB</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//【代码3】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;I am B&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;I am B&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="C"><a href="#C" class="headerlink" title="C"></a>C</h4><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">C</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">fC</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="comment">//【代码4】    //命令行窗口输出&quot;I am C&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">     System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;I am C&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">   &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="程序运行效果-1"><a href="#程序运行效果-1" class="headerlink" title="程序运行效果"></a>程序运行效果</h3><p><img src="data:image;base64,"></p>
<h3 id="记-1"><a href="#记-1" class="headerlink" title="记"></a>记</h3>]]></content>
